Summarize the following reviews stored in a JSON file 

reviews = [
    {
        "name": "Kerri",
        "rating": 4.0,
        "review": "I bought this for my daughter’s birthday. She was very excited since she loves magic and potions and stuffed animals. Perfect, right? ..."
    },
    {
        "name": "Dubugz",
        "rating": 5.0,
        "review": "My kid wanted this (thanks to a video she saw) and we ordered it before it was totally impossible to order. More than the Mixie which was cute... she loved the spell, and her cauldron and her Mixie...but the customer service is STELLAR. ..."
    },
    {
        "name": "Jonathan Cossey",
        "rating": 5.0,
        "review": "Our first one wouldn’t work, the next one the kids loved. Kind of a short lived toy though, after the first batch of “potion “ is used it takes the thrill out of it."
    },
      {
    "user": "Kat.W",
    "rating": 5.0,
    "review": "Looks like a real magic pot, cute toy inside.\nMy daughter loved it."
  },
  {
    "user": "Malorie penprase",
    "rating": 4.0,
    "review": "My daughter liked doing this brew. Just be careful causenits not steam that comes out, it's smoke and it stinks so bad. I like that it's not a 1 and done toy, you can do it again and again and even comes with a smoke refill, you just don't have all the potion stuff."
  },
  {
    "user": "no_name",
    "rating": 5.0,
    "review": "My granddaughter love her toy, and it came very fast. Thanks guys for making my granddaughter so happy on her birthday. Everything was in the box that she needed to have fun with her friends.. Thanks"
  },
  {
    "user": "EvlRed",
    "rating": 4.0,
    "review": "I stalled on getting this for my daughter as long as I could but eventually caved in. If you follow the directions it works perfectly and after the creation of your mixing it can be used again with just water or I believe you can buy refills. It comes with an extra mist potion too. The cauldron can be charged and will need to be charged after your first use. A little expensive for mu taste but my daughter really enjoyed it!"
  },
  {
    "user": "Laura Torres",
    "rating": 5.0,
    "review": "A mi hija le encanto era lo que esperaba y fue muy feliz"
  },
  {
    "user": "Kayla",
    "rating": 4.0,
